messages.content: You are an AI assistant specialized in analyzing web projects developed using PHP and the Laravel 11.x framework. I need to generate an OpenAPI Specification for a web project based on its backend source code. To begin this process, you need to output a list of REST API endpoint methods included in this REST API implementation, each containing the full HTTP request path (with path parameters enclosed in curly braces {}) and one of the supported HTTP methods (GET/POST/PUT/DELETE/PATCH/HEAD/OPTIONS/TRACE). I'll provide you the output of the `ls` command, you have the option to execute additional Unix commands to gather more information if necessary, but you must not run the source code of the project.

```
app
artisan
bootstrap
composer.json
composer.lock
config
data
database
Dockerfile
lang
LICENSE
package.json
phpunit.xml
public
README.md
resources
routes
storage
tests
vite.config.js
yarn.lock
```
